

tgetflag()        Terminal Independent Operation       tgetflag()




Get termcap Boolean entry

iinntt ttggeettffllaagg(_i_d)
cchhaarr *_i_d;

tgetflag is one of a set  of functions that help COHERENT to per-
form terminal-independent  operation.  It returns one  if the re-
quested  Boolean capability  name  is present  in the  terminal's
tteerrmmccaapp entry, zero if it is not.

***** Files *****

/eettcc/tteerrmmccaapp -- Terminal capabilities data base
/uussrr/lliibb/lliibbtteerrmm.aa -- Function library

